    <h4 class="desc">
      Forms and data input design patterns used throughout the app.
    </h4>
    <p>
      As the Product Designer I worked on wireframes, interaction design, user experience, and a design compositions for the application. I interfaced between internal stakeholders, product management, the scrum master, designers and engineers to bring out the final interface and interactions for the application.  We facilitated continuous user feedback within our iterations using interactive Balsamiq wireframes, user testing and group forums. My final deliverables included redlined designs, native assets, and a new SVG icon library for the hybrid portion of the application.
    </p>
    </div>
  <img src="<%= asset_path 'mobile_final.jpg' %>" class="wide-image"/>
