  <p>
    I worked with our Product Management and Marketing teams on our go to market strategy, and presented the new product at our annual user conference (BUC FEST). We created a range off assets for our sales team including a mobile landing page on the company website, demo instance, and sales video.  At 6 months after launch we have seen 300% growth of our end users accessing the application and a 98% decline in the use of the old application.  The internal team continues to iterate on the product and add new functionality.  As of 1/1/2015 we have released version 1.5.
    </p>
